# 🧩 System Components

### 🍕 Pizza Interface

Human control surface.

Allows users to:

• explore system modules
• visualise infrastructure
• trigger agent tasks
• inspect telemetry

---

### 🤖 Agent Layer

AI agents handle tasks such as:

• automation
• monitoring
• distributed compute
• system orchestration

---

### 📡 Telemetry Layer

Nodes stream system data such as:

• CPU usage
• memory
• network activity
• agent status

Telemetry feeds the dashboard in real time.

---

### 🖥 Hardware Nodes

Example nodes include:

```
Raspberry Pi agents
Mac workstations
GPU compute machines
Edge devices
```

These form the distributed compute layer.

