# 🧠 Design Philosophy

## Human-first AI interfaces

AI systems are becoming increasingly complex.

Most tools today rely on:

• CLI commands
• complicated dashboards
• fragmented monitoring tools

Aigent Pizza OS introduces a **simple visual control surface.**

---

## Visual modular thinking

Segmented visual systems help users understand infrastructure faster.

Benefits include:

• intuitive system navigation
• reduced cognitive load
• modular system design

---

## Spatial Interfaces

Many people reason about systems better visually than textually.

The pizza model creates a **mental map of infrastructure.**

